        <description>This title is a compilation of two timed puzzle-board games:
&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;i&gt;Reverse&lt;/i&gt; in which the player must turn the cubes in such a way as to cover the entire board. Indicating a single cube the player flips all the surrounding fields.
&lt;li&gt;&lt;i&gt;Misile Action&lt;/i&gt; in which the player must place four elements into the indicated destination area.  All objects move in the indicated direction until they are stopped by another element of the board. The additional bricks may be used as an assistance, but the player may encounter obstacles as well, such as deadly flames or magnets.
&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;</description>
